snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: The Shadowgazer - NCFC 2008 Montage
snippet.description:
Video montage of gameplay concepts introduced or reworked for my ongoing fan game 'The Shadowgazer'.

For more information visit:
http://www.zfgc.com/users/kingmob/index.html
http://www.zfgc.com/forum/index.php?topic=3937.0

... and, until 25th October 2008, you can show your support for The Shadowgazer (defending its Best In Show crown :P) at the annual Nintendo Community Fangame Convention at:
http://ncfc.taloncrossing.com/
